Battera::
She looked at Cybershark and blinked. She wasn't sure if  she was 
still dreaming or not. She looked around, seeing that she wasn't in 
the tank and she attacing sharkticons were not there. She looked back 
at CyberShark. "I, I think so." She turned her head to Vulois. "Is he 
going to be ok?"  She hugged CyberShark. She just wanted to make sure 
that this wasn't a dream. 



--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "David Torrey" <Dachande85@m...> wrote:
> ::CyberShark::
> 
>     He held Battera, she looked shaken up. Vulois hadn't awakened 
yet, or CyberShark hadn't noticed him.
>     "Are you all right?" He asked Battera.
